name: Nelson Dockland
description: Am Nelson I am independent, multicultural,down to earth, loving, friendly,outgoing, genuine, witty, playful, with a great intellect and sense of humor. Like a complex wine, I can be alternately sweet, tart, sparkling, or mellow I’m ultimately looking for a life partner, not just a casual date. I would like to meet someone that loves to travel,is positive, spontaneous, with a good sense of humor and a good conversationalist.
